{"tid":990713,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"窮人生仔，要你下賤生存一生","createTime":"2019-01-21T22:54:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T18:00:33.000Z","uid":40470,"like":100,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"29113d9b751d8af9065b201a15f1208be75d0c86","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T22:54:23.000Z","msg":"一出世<br />\n<br />\n你就係又嘈又爆滿公立醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成班老人除寒酸親戚拎住家頓雜餅送比你老母<br />\n<br />\n叫佢吸收多d營養出多d奶好好坐月<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人地有錢請陪月幫手臭b<br />\n<br />\n你就由兩件廢老用d清朝迷信方法養大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022825ec8ca482c766c1a10a02e92e070fe42d75","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T23:00:01.000Z","msg":"你呀嫲話你呀媽無奶水<br />\n<br />\n自己又揸又啜個你老母個奶頭話通奶比你飲<br />\n<br />\n你呀爺好肉緊又想幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你個廢柴窮老豆就企埋一二便睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n五個人包賣埋你，逼二百尺公屋，<br />\n<br />\n這就是你的獅子山下，你下賤人生的開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"accfd6a5bef381f784948a6e37e73e7a8e082b90","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T23:04:23.000Z","msg":"你呀爺話你有福有衣食<br />\n<br />\n因為一出世就有人送家頓雜餅，有食<br />\n<br />\n亦有四叔公留左一左堆好靚好新既舊衫比你著，得著<br />\n<br />\n你微絲細眼唇厚肉<br />\n<br />\n你爺話你似關帝將來必成人中之龍鳳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c139b4f492507480d01a10ec1f97f30421cd601","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":32,"dislike":3,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T23:15:34.000Z","msg":"你大左少少<br />\n<br />\n作為一個歲半既bb來講<br />\n<br />\n完全唔得意<br />\n<br />\n係孤兒院無人領養個種樣<br />\n<br />\n每次呀嫲餵你食粥<br />\n<br />\n佢都會都妹下d粥先比你食<br />\n<br />\n因為佢好驚有骨哽到你<br />\n<br />\n放心，佢好專業<br />\n<br />\n你呀嫲係鳳爪工場到做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bbcaa8f35f43dc83e54e1cd1cef2317ae6b5724","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T23:21:22.000Z","msg":"三歲喇<br />\n<br />\n你個柒頭仲呆呆滯滯<br />\n<br />\n人地三歲識a-z口齒伶俐<br />\n<br />\n你就乜柒都唔識唔出聲<br />\n<br />\n每日著住d寒酸舊衫望窗<br />\n<br />\n望住樓下公共公園d公屋窮細路粗野生存"},{"pid":"d36edf50d54dc4ca826f2038d4bc2513d625ebc3","tid":990713,"uid":107269,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T23:24:35.000Z","msg":"絕對係窮人生仔既寫照"},{"pid":"cd7555511c6b55b8b8e56696d76f89f4be240475","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T23:27:56.000Z","msg":"呆滯，零出聲，望窗<br />\n<br />\n最好玩既玩具<br />\n<br />\n係呀爺執返來既污糟膠袋同家頓雜餅空罐<br />\n<br />\n坐下坐下<br />\n<br />\n終於六歲<br />\n<br />\n你呀爺話香港政苦好有道義<br />\n<br />\n六歲就有免費書讀<br />\n<br />\n人人可成材"},{"pid":"364db12189c37dfdc9f08f778c1bb4048363adcd","tid":990713,"uid":38914,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T23:29:03.000Z","msg":"樓主個人寫照"},{"pid":"a4a1a514677da33971a8d3a6029642c5a28ac253","tid":990713,"uid":25902,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T23:32:05.000Z","msg":"岩啊 生左你出黎 又冇屋契比你搞到你比人串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38ef52fba7e7f0611131ca5046bb84ab1145d33","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T23:33:00.000Z","msg":"屋村小學<br />\n<br />\n理應大家都又窮又寒酸<br />\n<br />\n但港英殖民地政策<br />\n<br />\n就係幫你先安居，後樂業<br />\n<br />\n就算住公屋，都確實有人借利良策富起來<br />\n<br />\n但這總係人地既父母最好"},{"pid":"8c07837813254c7e9111c693b488ab6e7f7411ba","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T23:38:20.000Z","msg":"岩岩返小學，你矮人半個頭<br />\n<br />\n小息人地拎住兩蚊去小食部買媽咪面後仲有一蚊剩可以儲錢買玩具<br />\n<br />\n你<br />\n<br />\n永遠只有起屋企拎既家頓什餅頂肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你個鼻成日有流鼻涕<br />\n<br />\n無紙巾抹，由得佢乾<br />\n<br />\n久而久之<br />\n<br />\n同學幫你改左個花名叫鼻屎佬"},{"pid":"ea42eaee0b4d4f82373827c644fbec3dfe77157f","tid":990713,"uid":96826,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T23:39:54.000Z","msg":"樓主好憎嘉頓雜餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9312f3ec0f7c26876e948a15ee436c829bfb169","tid":990713,"uid":202278,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T23:41:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"196b003add2c2b76769b689c95243b72130621bd","tid":990713,"uid":56698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T23:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c94e71f171ea82a87ac2a94ef1bbe55e0805bf4","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T00:02:08.000Z","msg":"鼻屎佬！<br />\n<br />\n唔好過來呀唔比你玩！<br />\n<br />\n考完試，放聖誕假前既幾日<br />\n<br />\n對大部份小學生來講係最開心既<br />\n<br />\n因為可以帶玩具返學<br />\n<br />\n最受歡迎既一定係gameboy<br />\n<br />\n其次係變形金剛，魔神英雄傳<br />\n<br />\n鼻屎佬有乜玩具？<br />\n<br />\n一架勁舊既M記玩具車<br />\n<br />\n無人想同你交換玩<br />\n<br />\n無人想理你點好玩<br />\n<br />\n無人想你企得太近<br />\n<br />\n你企埋一二角前推後推你架價值接近零既玩具車<br />\n<br />\n事實上<br />\n<br />\n你手上既車仔<br />\n<br />\n價值比你現在既人生更高"},{"pid":"049ab039a0898b27598e496f1a21ce1779f86225","tid":990713,"uid":609,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T00:04:02.000Z","msg":"高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b82e84587024f416e390fef285399df428edd0","tid":990713,"uid":130280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T00:06:50.000Z","msg":"推到個仔100歲好辛苦咁係病房等死"},{"pid":"f99a7d5ad0cecb35ec1091e75a149933fed17d9e","tid":990713,"uid":174191,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T00:12:04.000Z","msg":"高汁 笑唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09c376b84d9ab6a3b8856d52492da350b7e9ccc","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T00:12:51.000Z","msg":"莫明其妙<br />\n<br />\n世界好似有無形既牆將人自自然然分隔"},{"pid":"da4308aa2ee778ec741c4b6d48bfeb0fc7bce75c","tid":990713,"uid":144738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T00:17:05.000Z","msg":"完全係窮人寫照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d3cb9e7f26662d43f810a4a77340c11c15ee3d2","tid":990713,"uid":121653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T00:18:27.000Z","msg":":<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d9c8e20ada962c799956b61eecb39d773f1ef1","tid":990713,"uid":80844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T00:35:21.000Z","msg":"睇到眼濕濕"},{"pid":"20afb213bad38d7468dd8ce86f5bb4badc1ede92","tid":990713,"uid":53538,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T00:41:59.000Z","msg":"跟住18歲中六合彩改變人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f8b019dfccb3648132f10ada0a24a0149b4595","tid":990713,"uid":16613,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T00:44:50.000Z","msg":"係咪因為樓主經歷過 所以可以寫得咁細緻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0233dc6eceaa2c2212481d1a2af2ca9dfba507","tid":990713,"uid":64009,"like":14,"dislike":18,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T00:47:37.000Z","msg":"樓主做咩係到寫自傳?<br />\n陰公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我細細個加拿大出世<br />\n小康之家<br />\n見到你依d經歷覺得你死左去好過"},{"pid":"698b9f22c38f0ddae97c08d3b98fc33d2f0cca77","tid":990713,"uid":125742,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T00:50:50.000Z","msg":"請利用嘉頓雜餅一詞寫出小時候你與家人如何呈現獅子山精神？ （50分）"},{"pid":"4f86d694eee715a62b701de337b3f7685935691c","tid":990713,"uid":35193,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T00:57:20.000Z","msg":"樓主應該好鍾意食嘉頓"},{"pid":"8e3928fd2d5b8b76c154dd4b8e97389e2779dff3","tid":990713,"uid":76747,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T00:59:06.000Z","msg":"月供股票改寫人生"},{"pid":"d16ae5220137ac8d9a6c41def3ffb6f01b06131d","tid":990713,"uid":136377,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:01:12.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6fb0808c14b8cd53833fb529ee0a1d83632831","tid":990713,"uid":208364,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21bc4bb436f8bc33fd66b47b2562be9e9de2a268","tid":990713,"uid":199692,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:06:12.000Z","msg":"識得三個醫生係屋邨出身"},{"pid":"400c10e6d35e34d48c70a1da48143be409dfd238","tid":990713,"uid":10382,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"21bc4bb436f8bc33fd66b47b2562be9e9de2a268","tid":990713,"uid":199692,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:06:12.000Z","msg":"識得三個醫生係屋邨出身"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:07:57.000Z","msg":"而家香港仲有幾多個尼d例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n彈一句出黎想點"},{"pid":"7c9a51dedf9592a5c5d549ac34d7f26f962e4206","tid":990713,"uid":212317,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:25:04.000Z","msg":"好慘  <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n住開太平山嘅我真系五明  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3578aae368c901b3132615d818bb90ff9dccf5d","tid":990713,"uid":170223,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"400c10e6d35e34d48c70a1da48143be409dfd238","tid":990713,"uid":10382,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"21bc4bb436f8bc33fd66b47b2562be9e9de2a268","tid":990713,"uid":199692,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:06:12.000Z","msg":"識得三個醫生係屋邨出身"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:07:57.000Z","msg":"而家香港仲有幾多個尼d例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n彈一句出黎想點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T02:09:30.000Z","msg":"咁又點 廿幾年黎比人笑 借錢讀書 讀到成隻狗咁先做到醫生目的就係脫貧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人生爸爸有錢 18歲有tesla揸 可以追夢 可以working holiday 洗鬼打份牛工 一啲都唔狠做專業人士呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569be37604b7d05c15176771da05dfd6a1aff43e","tid":990713,"uid":224871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T02:42:18.000Z","msg":"好撚慘 好有同感"},{"pid":"0c4ffa2b41a4a1a21ec35902797fd9776416ac67","tid":990713,"uid":16756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8e3928fd2d5b8b76c154dd4b8e97389e2779dff3","tid":990713,"uid":76747,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T00:59:06.000Z","msg":"月供股票改寫人生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T02:43:34.000Z","msg":"係 金銀業貿易場改寫人生"},{"pid":"54f32f464fb3df4828c0b6e6c439f8cae64521fb","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T04:58:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d607e9581dcef894fd2c7dff460874d72bf72912","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ea35b2ce0b0d333f3e33eca53f