id":85132,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:20:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0d77364a9992c11f81acb1e332343b50982dd58","tid":990713,"uid":105787,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:27:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afcff53a69546332bee96ff3692079d89ca53606","tid":990713,"uid":72487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc38e88d0f53fb923c6a2c158ec7368e2509905d","tid":990713,"uid":187584,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T15:22:48.000Z","msg":"最嬲係你老豆細個成日同你講，<br />\n嘉頓什餅係最好食既餅，<br />\n你睇，嘉頓wo!!! <br />\n個牌子好勁好出名架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲餅啲麵包好好食架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你話真係好難食，<br />\n佢就鬧你揀飲擇食，<br />\n知唔知你依家幾幸福，<br />\n佢細個食都無得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965e39785f8dce09c4e285e6aa3efc1dc88863c5","tid":990713,"uid":104004,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"364db12189c37dfdc9f08f778c1bb4048363adcd","tid":990713,"uid":38914,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T23:29:03.000Z","msg":"樓主個人寫照"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:51:02.000Z","msg":"留名睇屈鼠寫到自己4張野終於成為高級保安<br />\n呢篇野應該名為為&quot;屈機男之忿怒一生&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a36a4253658fd93ada922d0f3a23b1444a94182","tid":990713,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:47:33.000Z","msg":"寫到咁詳盡<br />\n睇黎經歷左唔少。。。"},{"pid":"653e3a4b1a73a6b48f664701452a047751fe8009","tid":990713,"uid":86545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T00:25:33.000Z","msg":"好好的文筆"},{"pid":"990f2eb9d26ede5960817f328bda73cf5cb2a2cf","tid":990713,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T01:06:47.000Z","msg":"樓主繼續寫！<br />\n好撚寫實<br />\n<br />\n以為係自己"},{"pid":"acb6a9222b678979a927b5466485d47343a5bb7e","tid":990713,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21bc4bb436f8bc33fd66b47b2562be9e9de2a268","tid":990713,"uid":199692,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:06:12.000Z","msg":"識得三個醫生係屋邨出身"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T01:10:40.000Z","msg":"一仗功成萬骨枯啫"},{"pid":"c5b53b9bf84d776c11f9c1e65658ce8f9367aad1","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:16:38.000Z","msg":"窮人既生活<br />\n<br />\n好平淡<br />\n<br />\n平淡到<br />\n<br />\n好似日日只可以食家頓雜餅既方形餅...同飲水<br />\n<br />\n不甘只食方形餅<br />\n<br />\n你去爭取，要威化，要夾心<br />\n<br />\n但你起呢個下賤既家庭中<br />\n<br />\n只係食物鏈最低層<br />\n<br />\n威化，夾心一早比你老豆收起自己食<br />\n<br />\n餅乾罐面總係咁美好，多種多樣<br />\n<br />\n可惜，這些機會不是屬於你的"},{"pid":"078185067f3ea8cb8139e38b0f1db4a7dabfff00","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:52:15.000Z","msg":"好多事，你明知做左<br />\n<br />\n都唔會對結果有任何影響<br />\n<br />\n但你必須去做<br />\n<br />\n目的，係比其他人睇，你有努力過<br />\n<br />\n雖然，真係唔會改變到結果<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一間垃圾屋村濕鳩小學<br />\n<br />\n仿效其他名校小學<br />\n<br />\n操練五六年級學生學能測驗<br />\n<br />\n為左可以令自校生升到名校中學<br />\n<br />\n你正常科目已經跟唔上<br />\n<br />\n再要去做不知所謂既學測選擇題<br />\n<br />\n你完全睇唔明問乜<br />\n<br />\n所以你每題都係亂填"},{"pid":"c4c3f6927e1811b12446e43ce7461ea8f69960a7","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:55:39.000Z","msg":"五揀一，六十題<br />\n<br />\n正常人亂填<br />\n<br />\n都會預期有十二分<br />\n<br />\n奇蹟既係<br />\n<br />\n你條柒頭每次都填滿晒<br />\n<br />\n但連續八次得分都係個位數"},{"pid":"d6cffa85636203769839a9c60bbeb41ad8681d1b","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:58:54.000Z","msg":"勵志書成日講<br />\n<br />\n人生<br />\n<br />\n就係被吸引力法則影響<br />\n<br />\n心態成功人士吸引財富，健康，快樂<br />\n<br />\n你確實就吸引到失敗，災難，自卑<br />\n<br />\n單睇模擬學能測驗成績，你確實如此"},{"pid":"26b1bcb9ebaebe9a8fbaa9f91bf789c1d471087d","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:03:08.000Z","msg":"有日操完學能測驗你返屋企<br />\n<br />\n見到你呀爺訓左起地下碌大雙眼不停抽搐"},{"pid":"f713c4e63ba13177689f1a077c695d83e1111d8c","tid":990713,"uid":46873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:05:52.000Z","msg":"樓主寫緊日記？"},{"pid":"a713160e12b63aa578b9b46c047db9c2aa45724a","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:11:12.000Z","msg":"眼角撞爆左，流血<br />\n<br />\n身體僵硬，口角有白泡<br />\n<br />\n你好驚，即刻走入廁所<br />\n<br />\n你呀嫲講過<br />\n<br />\n咁樣係鬼上身<br />\n<br />\n你知道屋企有鬼，你見過，成面血，條脷好長<br />\n<br />\n呀嫲話係祖先既鬼，本來做大官，比人害<br />\n<br />\n而家上左呀爺身"},{"pid":"5ae1ace6e0e4eb18de79393b061730e714c9d38d","tid":990713,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:12:51.000Z","msg":"等睇遲啲出嚟做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫人揾錢。"},{"pid":"733cd1d2687385faaabb4ee634c95df552451acb","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f713c4e63ba13177689f1a077c695d83e1111d8c","tid":990713,"uid":46873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:05:52.000Z","msg":"樓主寫緊日記？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071e8579262d64d39458b3cccb61bf1887952624","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ae1ace6e0e4eb18de79393b061730e714c9d38d","tid":990713,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:12:51.000Z","msg":"等睇遲啲出嚟做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫人揾錢。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:13:20.000Z","msg":"想做狗，都唔係人人有資格"},{"pid":"991308ff82a56aab726c318bc2be6331eaec8946","tid":990713,"uid":37599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:16:11.000Z","msg":"寫自傳？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf4fd672ce13e957b57ec02b4ef9bf13dc777985","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:16:57.000Z","msg":"痛苦既人生<br />\n<br />\n時間過得特別漫長<br />\n<br />\n一個人，起廁所<br />\n<br />\n好靜，好靜<br />\n<br />\n直至聽到呀嫲慘叫既聲...<br />\n<br />\n'老野你做咩？你唔好嚇我，唔好嚇我，呀呀呀噢'<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5291ef2d996291f2206a5d43096f6dc1edcf0b1b","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"991308ff82a56aab726c318bc2be6331eaec8946","tid":990713,"uid":37599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:16:11.000Z","msg":"寫自傳？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1713c7849faae5849bbca4a72f6f51b2bc0a3e9b","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:25:33.000Z","msg":"再有意識<br />\n<br />\n已經係坐起白車上<br />\n<br />\n你呀嫲不停喊，慘叫<br />\n<br />\n隔離坐左鄰居張師奶安慰佢<br />\n<br />\n救護員幫緊你呀爺急救<br />\n<br />\n全車最平靜係你<br />\n<br />\n你留意到你呀嫲賴左尿<br />\n<br />\n回想起細個你賴尿呀嫲都笑住幫你換褲<br />\n<br />\n你都會一齊笑<br />\n<br />\n過去，你曾經覺得賴尿都可以開心<br />\n<br />\n但此刻<br />\n<br />\n你知道賴尿一d都唔好笑"},{"pid":"5d61305fc5d89460a45ffa4dc58e770b1f8d9815","tid":990713,"uid":207059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:52:12.000Z","msg":"嘉頓欠咗樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a8f8df322c3d7584ea0419b662ead67b8a83ef","tid":990713,"uid":113360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T04:04:35.000Z","msg":"可唔可以繼續寫落去<br />\n我想知我未來係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd096bf2384925f75b28c211e7fbcf5bff9c374","tid":990713,"uid":25676,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e1a8f8df322c3d7584ea0419b662ead67b8a83ef","tid":990713,"uid":113360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T04:04:35.000Z","msg":"可唔可以繼續寫落去<br />\n我想知我未來係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T04:16:49.000Z","msg":"窮人唔會有未來"},{"pid":"7696eba0f151224e06ea9e20368c40e54298bcbe","tid":990713,"uid":148189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T05:36:25.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"ac9b9b9f0bbfe8befdaae1ee035dd2ce17c16f07","tid":990713,"uid":29008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T05:50:04.000Z","msg":"今次寫得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嘉頓什餅買一罐夠養大你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea921ccbd8bb9fa1210872cd07306658a90a847","tid":990713,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T07:06:36.000Z","msg":"收聲呀 唔撚好再講"},{"pid":"93a680bdd1d3bc47f663775d5720dda8a9efbe0e","tid":990713,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T08:05:18.000Z","msg":"繼續樓主！"},{"pid":"ef20ecd02babed4699ec02c986eb6920d771ef53","tid":990713,"uid":62990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T08:14:15.000Z","msg":"Live咗 有啲浮誇 但幾好睇<br />\nLm待睇 加油樓豬"},{"pid":"f0e39c77ace9e9a4b3303f7876f97b3284c3b360","tid":990713,"uid":88763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T08:16:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8680/16285590485_42ae455d7d_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm9.staticflickr.com%2F8680%2F16285590485_42ae455d7d_o.jpg&h=85dc5ea2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16abf7c51b391e9ef958dad93cb31f01111ad744","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T09:36:16.000Z","msg":"呀爺就咁就去左無返過來<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以前<br />\n<br />\n呀爺話你係關羽轉世<br />\n<br />\n佢就自稱諸葛亮，因佢懂天文，識地理<br />\n<br />\n假若<br />\n<br />\n爺孫二人並肩而行<br />\n<br />\n一文一武<br />\n<br />\n無堅不摧<br />\n<br />\n天下可得<br />\n<br />\n確實<br />\n<br />\n每逢呀爺帶你去公園玩<br />\n<br />\n必定爭到千秋玩<br />\n<br />\n同親呀爺搭巴士<br />\n<br />\n必定爭到位坐，仲要係窗口位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無喇<br />\n<br />\n呀爺死左<br />\n<br />\n無喇<br />\n<br />\n以後都無喇"},{"pid":"78e13556e5a95d0973869b2273239dc299fba080","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T09:47:28.000Z","msg":"呀爺死左<br />\n<br />\n喊左好多次<br />\n<br />\n真係好多次<br />\n<br />\n數學堂喊，中文堂喊，聖經堂喊<br />\n<br />\n多左個強化版既花名<br />\n<br />\n喊包鼻屎佬"},{"pid":"366ad64d3b208b65e216fd00e48d0dc8cd3258d3","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T09:52:13.000Z","msg":"喊得太多<br />\n<br />\n上上下堂比訓導主任叫左去校長室<br />\n<br />\n校長叫左呀嫲來接你<br />\n<br />\n諗住可以返屋企<br />\n<br />\n點知呀嫲帶左你去紙扎鋪"},{"pid":"8f4dcd186eee13ac1e286cf53645d755f5de2cae","tid":990713,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"366ad64d3b208b65e216fd00e48d0dc8cd3258d3","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T09:52:13.000Z","msg":"喊得太多<br />\n<br />\n上上下堂比訓導主任叫左去校長室<br />\n<br />\n校長叫左呀嫲來接你<br />\n<br />\n諗住可以返屋企<br />\n<br />\n點知呀嫲帶左你去紙扎鋪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T09:54:11.000Z","msg":"繼續樓主"},{"pid":"6a95642a6b356c8f2df4d686c1876b5c011db40a","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T10:00:43.000Z","msg":"呀嫲話你比呀爺隻鬼攪<br />\n<br />\n佢半夜見到呀爺伸長條脷奶你塊面吸你魂魄<br />\n<br />\n紙扎鋪老闆一算<br />\n<br />\n原來呀爺死既時辰係極陰之時<br />\n<br />\n呀爺橫死變左勵鬼，必害你全家<br />\n<br />\n要比二千蚊攪法事七日先可以化劫"},{"pid":"c26a9b25d9192179ca846b6981bff91e814fb940","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T10:05:25.000Z","msg":"窮人使錢<br />\n<br />\n真係特別冤枉<br />\n<br />\n平時一個幾毫慳埋慳埋<br />\n<br />\n某日就會有勵鬼鍊住你條頸<br />\n<br />\n要你嘔返d錢出來"},{"pid":"1a0760dd71eef454992637380be84ae4ec58c18e","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T10:07:36.000Z","msg":"印象中<br />\n<br />\n你見過呢個人<br />\n<br />\n但你又講唔出佢係邊個<br />\n<br />\n好默生<br />\n<br />\n但你知你見過佢"},{"pid":"d46695f257c9e1542168beb17f230b2d32e56f23","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T10:10:18.000Z","msg":"呀爺死左<br />\n<br />\n呢個人就出現<br />\n<br />\n平時飯枱對住電視個位一定係呀爺坐<br />\n<br />\n今日呢個人，坐左個位"},{"pid":"934fa4946234b75932ff47c17c49141a87f4e233","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T10:16:26.000Z","msg":"留低左幾多錢？<br />\n<br />\n佢d錢應該全部係我既<br />\n<br />\n快d行，拎個圖章<br />\n<br />\n銀行就閂門，趁早攞晒d錢比我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢次係你一生人最後一次見呢個人"},{"pid":"8be96ff61b89b70055e882c5973c1125a9e18a57","tid":990713,"uid":25676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:19:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好默生<br />\n<br />\n但你知你見過佢</blockquote><br />\n陌生"},{"pid":"d80a58483b0a0a0c6f9342c50449dd6db49774e9","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8be96ff61b89b70055e882c5973c1125a9e18a57","tid":990713,"uid":25676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:19:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好默生<br />\n<br />\n但你知你見過佢</blockquote><br />\n陌生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:51:51.000Z","msg":"我係degree holder<br />\n<br />\n香港人中文水平低下"},{"pid":"5aa3e1885e70209f39dc3723a7adc20e329b335f","tid":990713,"uid":83060,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:57:05.000Z","msg":"生育呢個行為其實同強姦無乜分別，<br />\n同樣係唔理會受者 ( 子女、被姦者 ) 感受，<br />\n強行做出一個行為 ( 生育，插入 )<br />\n最後受者有機會出現快樂、感恩 ( 報答父母，愛上強姦犯 )，<br />\n或痛苦一生 ( 怨恨、抑鬱 )<br />\n<br />\n而不論結果係快樂定痛苦，生育的人都是在賭博，<br />\n因為天下間沒有父母可以確保子女幸福快樂，<br />\n否則蔡志明個女就唔駛燒炭死。<br />\n賭贏，則人有我有、養兒防老、有仔送終，<br />\n賭輸，則子女痛苦一生。<br />\n<br />\n所以天下父母皆自私，我地可以將天下父母視為強姦犯一樣鄙視及唾罵。"},{"pid":"9d82af26f4d7a00f0ee6f89723765167f5503aba","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aa3e1885e70209f39dc3723a7adc20e329b335f","tid":990713,"uid":83060,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:57:05.000Z","msg":"生育呢個行為其實同強姦無乜分別，<br />\n同樣係唔理會受者 ( 子女、被姦者 ) 感受，<br />\n強行做出一個行為 ( 生育，插入 )<br />\n最後受者有機會出現快樂、感恩 ( 報答父母，愛上強姦犯 )，<br />\n或痛苦一生 ( 怨恨、抑鬱 )<br />\n<br />\n而不論結果係快樂定痛苦，生育的人都是在賭博，<br />\n因為天下間沒有父母可以確保子女幸福快樂，<br />\n否則蔡志明個女就唔駛燒炭死。<br />\n賭贏，則人有我有、養兒防老、有仔送終，<br />\n賭輸，則子女痛苦一生。<br />\n<br />\n所以天下父母皆自私，我地可以將天下父母視為強姦犯一樣鄙視及唾罵。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T12:07:52.000Z","msg":"「父母未經我同意就生下我」男要把父母告上法庭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1005651\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1005651</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e9bf1a70b6c2f3d5a92e4eaf99c96461791bbac3","tid":990713,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T12:15:49.000Z","msg":"出快少少 live緊"},{"pid":"778a71ea24827603a9014b462347cfcf6ebe9c99","tid":990713,"uid":90403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a81ffedeea5473bcf02707d13c12afb8299721cc","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"c09c376b84d9ab6a3b8856d52492da350b7e9ccc","tid":990713,"uid":40470,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T00:12:51.000Z","msg":"莫明其妙<br />\n<br />\n世界好似有無形既牆將人自自然然分隔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T19:32:36.000Z","msg":"體育堂分組無人同你一組<br />\n<br />\n人地小息玩捉你就企埋一二便<br />\n<br />\n漸漸，唔多出聲既你<br />\n<br />\n更加唔出聲<br />\n<br />\n其他人望你郁都唔郁<br />\n<br />\n但你個腦轉